    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "> Oh.... why is that?\n\nBecause codemirror will lose focus. And it triggers side effect of command mode, scolling, and all these annoying things. \n\nWe won't add tabindex, as keyboard user can use keyboard shortcut. Keyboard user will not \"navigate\" to button with keyboard. Most of the action do have effect on \"selected\" cell. So trying to add accessibility to these buttons is a non-issue. Well, with more work, which is on it's way button could have also at title text the shortcut to trigger them. \n"
